    <font face="Arial,Helvetica,Geneva,Swiss,SunSans-Regular" size="2"><br><br>
    A new checkbox "Include Full Address History" has been added to Advanced Person Search to provide you greater control of historical address views -- even when your search criteria is narrow (i.e., when name plus state are entered as search terms). So, when this box is checked, full address history will be returned, not limited to the address, city and/ or state submitted in the search form.
